.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Contains configuration files.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB/var/ocm/ccr/log\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Contains log files.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB/var/ocm/ccr/state\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Contains state files and collected data.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB/var/ocm/ccr/state/review/targetMap.xml\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Summaries of the data that was collected.
.RE

.sp
.ne 2
.mk
.na
\fB\fB/var/ocm/ccr/state/review\fR\fR
.ad
.sp .6
.RS 4n
Data that was collected by the OCM.
.RE

